original: The scattered remnants of civilization, these lucky few managed to barricade themselves inside during the earliest stages of the Cataclysm.  Although temporarily secure, they are short on supplies and lack the skills to obtain more.  It's only a matter of time before they too become the prey of otherwordly creatures, or of all-too-human monsters.
translation: 人类文明的残存幸存者，少数幸运的人在大灾变初期成功搭建了安全屋并活了下来。虽然暂时安全，但是他们缺少补给及获得更多补给的能力。对他们来说，成为种种异界生物或是“那些人”的晚餐只是时间问题。
